creator: 1st for Women
descriptionHtml:
In-app crash detection, emergency medical assistance and so much more. If you have comprehensive; off-road; third party, fire & theft; motorcycle; and third party only cover from 1st for Women, you automatically get Guardian Angel on Call to help keep you safe on the road. Depending on your cover, this service includes:

CRASH DETECTION: An in-app mobile crash detector picks up if you’re in a severe accident.

EMERGENCY MEDICAL ASSISTANCE: Emergency medical assistance sent to your exact location, whether you contact us or not.

TOWING SERVICE: An authorised tow-truck sent to your exact location. The ability to view driver details and track their progress in app.

ROADSIDE ASSISTANCE: A roadside assistance provider that you can track to your exact location if your vehicle is out of fuel, has a flat battery, or a flat tyre.

REQUEST A LIFT: If your vehicle is towed, you can request a lift to where you need to go.

STAND-BY ME SERVICE: If you’re feeling unsafe, a Guardian Angel will be sent to wait with you until help arrives.

AUTOMATIC CLAIMS NOTIFICATION: Our claims team will be notified immediately of your accident. Customers with comprehensive and off-road vehicle cover benefit from all the services above and can share them with their regular drivers and up to five loved ones.

All 1st for Women customers can view their policy details on the 1st for Women app.
